{"title":"Scott Patron eRide long-travel eMTB boasts next-level integration with hidden shock","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/07/scott-patron-eride-long-travel-emtb-boasts-next-level-integration-with-hidden-shock/","date":1631013191000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-270644\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Scott have added an all-new eMTB to their line-up; the Scott Patron eRide. In terms of travel, it slots between the Genius eRide and Ransom eRide, but boasts a bigger battery than both, with a Bosch Performance Line CX motor that is uniquely rotated backwards to accommodate a four-bar linkage that drives a shock hidden away inside the top tube. Such integration is nothing new for Scott, having adapted <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/05/23/scott-sports-makes-a-bold-partnership-with-indie-mountain-bike-brand/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bold’s technology</a> to create their World Championship winning <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/09/2022-scott-spark-gets-bold-new-redesign-as-a-slack-fast-fully-integrated-120mm-xc-bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Scott Spark</a>. Here’s how they’ve adapted it to a long travel eMTB.</p><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KNefbwqzMKU?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" ezoid=\"0.2454890793255493\"></iframe></p><h2>Scott Patron eRide eMTB</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration.jpg\" alt=\"SCOTT PATRON ERIDE EMTB\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051633/scott-patron-eride-emtb-top-tube-shock-integration-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>The Scott Patron eRide eMTB runs 160mm travel, front and rear, with the latter delivered by a four-bar linkage driving a top tube integrated shock. While it sure does look very neat, tidy and impressive, the integration is about more than aesthetics. Hiding the shock inside the frame opens up space within the front triangle to accommodate the motor and a full size water bottle. There is also the added benefit of keeping trail crud away from the shock wiper seal.&nbsp;</p><div id=\"attachment_270698\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-270698\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon.jpg\" alt=\"scott patron eride emtb integrated shock twin-loc lockout syncros hixon one-piece stem handlebar assembly\" width=\"1600\" height=\"530\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon-297x98.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon-800x265.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon-120x40.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon-768x254.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon-1536x509.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon-297x98.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon-800x265.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon-120x40.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon-768x254.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07054213/scott-patron-eride-emtb-twin-loch-shock-lockout-integrated-cable-routing-headset-syncros-hixon-1536x509.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-270698\">The new Syncros Hixon IC SL one-piece bar and stem headset assembly feeds brake hoses, a gear cable, Twin-Loc suspension and dropper cables, Bosch remote and KIOX 300 Display cables directly into the front triangle to keep the cockpit as uncluttered as possible</p></div><p>The FOX Nude shock can be be switched between three different modes using Scott’s Twin-Loc system, with cables internally routed up through the top tube and onto the handlebar mounted remote via the updated Syncros Hixon IC SL one-piece stem and handlebar. Those modes are Lockout, Traction Control and Descend; rear wheel travel is reduced to 115mm in Lockout mode. For air pressure and rebound adjustments, the shock can be accessed via a removable panel on the underside of the top tube.</p><div id=\"attachment_270701\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-270701\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights.jpg\" alt=\"scott patron eride emtb rear light integration\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07064256/scott-patron-eride-lights-1536x864.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-270701\">The integration doesn’t end there; the Scott Patron eRide eMTB also gets integrated rear light on the seat stays. There’s also a custom rear fender to prevent the creation of a loam shelf</p></div><h3>A look inside</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy.jpg\" alt=\"scott patron eride emtb transparent frame\" width=\"1600\" height=\"933\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy-800x467.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy-768x448.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy-1536x896.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy-800x467.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy-768x448.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051644/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-Copy-1536x896.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>This image of a transparent frame helps us make better sense of it all, showing how the cables are routed internally, how the 205mm x 60mm shock is mounted inside the top tube, how the Bosch Performance Line CX motor is uniquely tilted backwards within its housing, and how the 750Wh battery slides into the downtube just forward of the motor.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy.jpg\" alt=\"scott patron eride emtb shock suspension layout\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051647/scott-patron-eride-emtb-transparent-frame-hidden-shock-Copy-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>Taking a closer look, we can see how the four-bar linkage drives the shock via a linkage that is hidden within the front triangle, where the top tube and seat tube flow into one another. Scott tells us the kinematic of the Patron eRide was designed specifically around Bosch’s latest eMTB motor. The drive unit has been rotated by 46° and is now supported from underneath for improved integration, increased stiffness and improved heat management.</p><div id=\"attachment_270691\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-270691\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through.jpg\" alt=\"scott patron erode hidden shock view\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1066\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through-1536x1023.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07051627/scott-patron-eride-emtb-hidden-shock-top-tube-see-through-1536x1023.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-270691\">The Bosch Performance Line XC motor delivers up to 85Nm torque; with the 750Wh battery, the Patron eRide has a claimed 100 km range</p></div><h3>Scott Patron eRide Geometry</h3><div id=\"attachment_270700\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-270700\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb.jpg\" alt=\"scott patron eride 900 tuned\" width=\"1600\" height=\"933\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb-800x467.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb-768x448.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb-1536x896.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb-800x467.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb-768x448.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07063632/scott-patron-eride-emtb-1536x896.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-270700\">The Scott Patron eRide 900 Tuned retails at 8,699 €</p></div><p>The Scott Patron eRide eMTB rolls on 29″ wheels with fixed geometry. It gets 454mm chainstays across the S-XL size range with reach figures stretching from 432.7mm to 501.2mm. The head angle sits at 65° on the M-XL frames, slightly slacker at 64.5° on the S frame. Seat tube angles are all appropriately upright starting at 77° on the Small, slackening ever so slightly to 76.8° on the XL.</p><p>The bottom bracket sits at a height of 347mm across the board, with 165mm crank arms on all sizes.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry.jpg\" alt=\"scott patron emtb geometry chart\" width=\"1400\" height=\"816\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry-800x466.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry-800x466.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07062844/scott-patron-e-ride-geometry-768x448.jpg 768w\"></a></p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><div id=\"attachment_270703\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07070055/scott-patron-eride-920-orange.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-270703\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07070055/scott-patron-eride-920-orange.jpg\" alt=\"scott patron eride 920 orange\" width=\"1600\" height=\"933\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07070055/scott-patron-eride-920-orange.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07070055/scott-patron-eride-920-orange-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07070055/scott-patron-eride-920-orange-800x467.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07070055/scott-patron-eride-920-orange-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/07070055/scott-patron-eride-920-orange-768x448.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com